    <enum name="ONBOARD_POSE_ESTIMATION_SOURCE" bitmask="true">
      <description>Bitmask of positioning sources currently active and being fused by the OBC EKF. Multiple sources may be active simultaneously. Reported in ONBOARD_POSE_ESTIMATION_STATUS.active_sources. Bits 5-31 reserved for future Avestec use.</description>
